slike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:45:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f83d8291e359c859a8c5771eff157fcf2b83626a","tid":1556154,"uid":8600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:01:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1555513/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1555513/page/1</a><br />\n幫推下,連儂牆文宣好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有地區勇武力量"},{"pid":"564a5ed7630463e073680bcae6b7abd80adc1897","tid":1556154,"uid":250889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:04:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fab4b89238d80da38191790d5bdc33b8220e70ef","tid":1556154,"uid":250889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:04:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73c667240578c5adff55903e323cb4e11af9f312","tid":1556154,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:50:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"809d5d120c12819fa70e59ce96ba5e9c48b5816a","tid":1556154,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:50:11.000Z","msg":"有咩要幫手？"},{"pid":"69d2ffa7ea0556531b06417062c14a7e1948c924","tid":1556154,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:50:42.000Z","msg":"連儂牆啲嘢唔見晒"},{"pid":"610479fa4d69f7293eb426112c06d098f2365649","tid":1556154,"uid":15745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:51:11.000Z","msg":"【攬炒戰線！尋求美國軍事保護！】<br />\n<br />\nIf we BURN！You！burn with Us！🔥🔥🚔🚊🔥🔥<br />\nReally！？講就兇狠！叫你簽個名，你就笠晒水!<br />\n<br />\n請求美國軍事保護，讓香港國民免於屠殺。<br />\n香港人！想唔想睇班死差佬真係死狗咁，跪低求饒咁撚樣！想！就大大力簽！<br />\n<br />\n聯署最後一日，條數雖得二萬七，但比賽一日未完結都唔會放棄！盡推！<br />\n<br />\n白宮聯署連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/send-military-force-hong-kong-save-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-beginning-11-aug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsend-military-force-hong-kong-save-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-beginning-11-aug&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNvzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=81d7bf76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/send-military-force-hong-kong-save-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-beginning-11-aug</a><br />\n<br />\n步驟：<br />\n<br />\n1. 簽 <br />\n2. 查電郵確認 <br />\n3. Share去十個fb、whatsaap、tg group"},{"pid":"c7412eea945ad38281acbc6035ae19b542a3f7ff","tid":1556154,"uid":225100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:51:32.000Z","msg":"一定要推爆<span style=\"color: red;\">願榮光歸香港</span><br />\n參考沙田太古<br />\n我哋依加要開展社區戰線<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0sBTyU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0sBTyU4.jpg&h=de779003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隨身帶備歌詞派/airdrop俾途人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要入屋!!</span>"},{"pid":"fddd5bb1c2147459e58337b652214736df199cec","tid":1556154,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b74beb7b5046246385dbc3d0b6edb31b0b596e8","tid":1556154,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:53:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4185c554620aa6b1921bc160e902f3ec4cfd6a4b","tid":1556154,"uid":47509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:53:37.000Z","msg":"自己區自己貼 唔好依賴人<br />\n印幾張 貼自己樓下都已經好成功"},{"pid":"6b8de10860657cfb070e033542dd9e9e88d52d9a","tid":1556154,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:58:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5421f378a088fb1a7e7eaf4c50cb5351e55f1aa4","tid":1556154,"uid":263068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"